          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1670922952093-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion has softened, add the <strong>drained noodles </strong>to the pan with the <strong>pho stock </strong>and<strong> remaining tamari soy sauce </strong>and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, cook for 1-2 min or until the noodles are completely tender, then remove from the heat and add the juice of <strong>half</strong> your <strong>lime[s] </strong>– this is your <strong>fragrant</strong> <strong>pho</strong></p><p>Cut the<strong> remaining lime </strong>into 1 wedge per person</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1670922958715-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1670922958715-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1670922958715-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1670922958715-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1670922958715-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>fragrant</strong> <strong>pho</strong> topped with the <strong>crispy tofu</strong>, <strong>chopped coriander</strong>,<strong> mint leaves </strong>and <strong>stems</strong> and the<strong> carrot matchsticks</strong></p><p>Drizzle over your<strong> sriracha </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and<strong> </strong>garnish with a<strong> lime wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
